================================================================================
Companion repositories
================================================================================

The full AgenticSTS release spans three repositories that interoperate:

  * AgenticSTS (this repo) — agent code, static game knowledge, paper
    artifact bundle.

  * AgenticSTS-Data — dynamic data: 298 game trajectories from the EMNLP 2026
    paper, frozen L4/L5 memory snapshots at SHA 1888a62, analysis scripts.
    Released under CC-BY-4.0.

  * AgenticSTS-Mod — the Godot 4.5 / .NET 9 Slay the Spire 2 mod that
    exposes the REST/MCP gameplay interface used by this agent.

